Package at.ac.tuwien.ict.andropicar.rmcs.data

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IControlData
    A general class for all classes used to store control-data.
    Although the class itself does not provide any functionality (does not have attributes or methods), it is necessary to have a common class for the LinkedBlockingQueues that are used to send control-data-sets between the different modules / threads.
    IData  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CameraControlData
    Contains one set of values for controlling the RMCSs camera rotation.
    DistanceSensorData
    Contains one set of values of the RMCSs distance-sensors.
    DriveControlData
    Contains one set of values for controlling the RMCSs drive (acceleration/velocity and steering).
    LightControlData
    Contains one set of values for controlling the RMCSs lights (front / back, winkers).
    SensorData  
    UniqueLinkedBlockingQueue<E>
    An extension of the LinkedBlockingQueue that adds the functionality of only allowing one Object per class in the queue.
    VelocitySensorData
    Contains one set of values of the RMCSs velocity-sensors.
